meta.title: Abigail dies while walking home in white slippers.

bubble.text: Dude, I have so many questions.
But the most important one is..
WHY IS THIS EVEN A THING?!
These two sound like those people from the milkman conspiracy in Psychonauts.
Seriously though, I'm getting tired of your fetishes.
